text: Maha Haddioui (; born 15 May 1988) is a Moroccan professional golfer who plays on the Ladies European Tour. She is the first Arab with playing privileges on the Ladies European Tour. She attended Lynn University, where she was the top- ranked golfer in NCAA Division II. Haddioui qualified for the 2016 Summer Olympics.
